on of ions that have traversed the\nmagnetic presheath is obtained, which is important to predict the amount of\nsputtering and erosion at the wall of a fusion device.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 24 Nov 2018 22:05:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-27"}
